  "text": "The effect of indole on biofilm formation was investigated as described by [CITATION_1] . Overnight strains of V. fischeri ETJB1H and ibpA À were subcultured in 96-well microplates with LBS media (with 0.25, 0.5 and 1.0 mM indole) and incubated at 28°C for 18 h. The crystal violet assay was used for quantification of biofilm. All assays were performed in triplicate.",
